description: Open House Saturday 1/11 cancelled - Offer has been accepted.  Fresh new look to this incredible penthouse two-bedroom.  Updates to this unit include:  Refinished Floors, Refaced Cabinets, and fresh Wall to Wall Paint Job.   This well laid out condo has a very live-able floor plan with 2 equal sized bedrooms.  Off the kitchen is an oversized deck allowing for maximum entertaining space with a spiral staircase that leads to private roof deck.  This a great rental alternative as well as an incredible investment opportunity.  Located at the corner of F st, just a few blocks from West Broadway, the T, the beach, and South Boston's bar & restaurant scene.
